Windfish (EtsunaZeldaDX)
        Menu -> Start Game
   =>   Start House -> Start House -> Mabe Village
   =>   Mabe Village -> Mabe Village -> Forest
   =>   Forest -> Forest -> Graveyard
   =>   Graveyard -> Graveyard -> No Name 5
   =>   No Name 5 -> No Name 5 -> Nightmare
   =>   Nightmare -> Nightmare -> Windfish
   =>   Windfish
Witch Item (Koholint Prairie) (EtsunaZeldaDX)
        Menu -> Start Game
   =>   Start House -> Start House -> Mabe Village
   =>   Mabe Village -> Mabe Village -> Forest
   =>   Forest -> Forest -> No Name 82
   =>   No Name 82 -> No Name 82 -> Witch Item (Koholint Prairie)
   =>   Witch Item (Koholint Prairie)
